Package: dlayr
Type: Package
Title: Calculate public transit delays based on the General Transit Feed Specification (GTFS) and a real time gps feed. 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hans Thompson
Maintainer: Hans Thompson <hans.thompson1@gmail.com>
Description: This package calculates the delays that google and third party apps want to show real time information on the public transit vechicle status. 
    This package allows the delays to be output as a protocol buffer, json api, or a web map. 
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: dplyr,
    lubridate,
    tidyr,
    gtfsr
Remotes: ropensci/gtfsr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
